msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "3D0 controller"
msgstr "Ovladač 3DO"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The 3DO Interactive Multiplayer is a game console developed by the 3DO Company. Panasonic produced the first models in 1993, and further models were released by Sanyo and GoldStar (now LG) in 1994."
msgstr "3DO Interactive Multiplayer je herní konzole vyvinutá společností The 3DO Company. První modely vyrobila v roce 1993 společnost Panasonic, další modely pak v roce 1994 vydaly společnosti Sanyo a GoldStar (dnes LG)."

